{"tid":1938312,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"X偏方 全民拆解II[粵]    ","createTime":"2020-03-22T12:35:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-28T12:34:43.000Z","uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3e48c36a9a7e76fe89937a685b751ea5c0a5ceae","tid":1938312,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T12:35:58.000Z","msg":"X偏方 全民拆解II[粵]&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n陸浩明(六號)、孫慧雪、李旻芳、余德丞率先拆解坊間的止咳偏方。洋蔥蘋果水有助舒緩咳嗽？關鍵在於洋蔥蘊藏檞皮素，但為何還需配合蘋果？中醫學認為以薑擦背亦能止咳，留意醫師指示的正確穴位。「街頭偏方」由德丞搜羅坊間的羅漢果茶飲，老字號羅漢果茶、即沖羅漢甘果茶、陳皮紅棗羅漢果茶各有甚麼功效？六號採用白蘿蔔、蜂蜜製作日本人的止咳偏方；女中醫並細談白蘿蔔「破氣」之說。另外，蜂蜜咖啡、黑朱古力亦可舒緩咳嗽？"},{"pid":"34690688a1431424b01edfff1124dde119108915","tid":1938312,"uid":412,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T12:48:46.000Z","msg":"屌"},{"pid":"d49fd5ebeb87cef807573b0d070dc6d78e6237a6","tid":1938312,"uid":412,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T12:49:08.000Z","msg":"樓主躝開啦"},{"pid":"88f7058dcb9793fe2d9d1c2e728b37d8bc5f48df","tid":1938312,"uid":412,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T12:49:29.000Z","msg":"樓主老母畀狗屌"},{"pid":"2b6800f5860bf51d87ad6b225080bce32e1bf2e3","tid":1938312,"uid":412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T12:50:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>連<br />\n登<br />\n日<br />\n報<br />\n｜<br />\n支<br />\n持<br />\n獨<br />\n裁<br />\n政<br />\n權<br />\n者<br />\n，<br />\n無<br />\n權<br />\n享<br />\n有<br />\n言<br />\n論<br />\n自<br />\n由</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1180589\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1180589</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">請<br />\n問<br />\nNew_God_美斯<br />\n(會員#38456)<br />\n你<br />\n屙<br />\n尿<br />\n嗰<br />\n陣<br />\n起<br />\n左<br />\n腳<br />\n定<br />\n右<br />\n腳<br />\n?</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1646963\" data-auto-link targ